<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٥٥٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْعَلَاءِ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5879">ابْنُ فُضَيْلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4642">عُمَارَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/268">أَبِي زُرْعَةَ، </a>سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ:</span> قَالَ اللهُ <span class="special">﷿</span>: <span class="c2">«وَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ مِمَّنْ ذَهَبَ يَخْلُقُ كَخَلْقِي، فَلْيَخْلُقُوا ذَرَّةً أَوْ لِيَخْلُقُوا حَبَّةً أَوْ شَعِيرَةً.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>